<HEADLINE>
ATTENDANTS UNION WAITING FOR BETTER OFFER FROM AMWEST 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By PETER CORBETT  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
