8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   MUSIC-NOTES _ Will lede with a bit on the Washington-area opera
``Where Angels Fear to Tread,'' based on E.M. Forster, music by
Mark Lanz Weiser, an up-and-coming composer. Plus other items.
(Green, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
