<P>
   FASHION-HAIR _ NEW YORK _ On the runway, hair can be an
extension of a designer's look. Then again, sometimes it's just
hair extensions. The last day of Fashion Week featured some heavy
hitters _ Calvin Klein, Vera Wang, Han Feng and Donna Karan. Here
is a peek at what their hairstylists whipped up, and why. (Anna,
Palm Beach Post). MOVED.
