r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CRUEL-REVIEW-LADN     03-04 0682
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CRUEL-REVIEW-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`CRUEL INTENTIONS' A STEAMY BET
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
OUR RATING: 4 STARS 
By BOB STRAUSS  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR; LOS ANGELES _ At least Sarah Michelle Gellar and Ryan
