<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990304.0130 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-04 13:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7567 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHILDCARE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      03-04 1661
