<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-04 13:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7570 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LYNCH-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      03-04 0695
