<P>
   INVEST-AVIATION-NYT (Undated) _ Aviation services stocks offer a
compelling story. By Michelle Leder.
</P>
<P>
   ONBUSINESS-COLUMN-BOS (Undated) _ The question of the day: How
worried should we be about day trading and what should we do about
it? By Steven Syre and Charles Stein.
</P>
