<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Visit tourism offices for travel information
 &HT;    EDs: Embargoed for Sunday, March, 7.
 &HT;    By Paula Crouch Thrasher
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Most states and U.S. territories have tourism offices.
</P>
<P>
   If requesting travel literature, be as specific as possible.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Alabama: Alabama Bureau of Tourism and Travel, 401 Adams Ave.,
Suite 126, Montgomery, AL 36104;
