<P>
   .travelsc.com.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  South Dakota: South Dakota Department of Tourism, 711 E. Wells
Ave., Pierre, SD 57501; 1-800-732-5682, fax 605-773-3256,
http://www.state.sd.us.
