<HEADLINE>
LAWMAKERS INTRODUCE AIRLINE COMPETITION LEGISLATION. 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (EDs: FILED in ``f'' and ``w'' categories)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
