   The obituary of Otumfuo Opoku Ware II, sent by the New York
Times News Service on Wednesday, Mar. 3, misstated his age in some
editions. He was 79, not 89. The obituary also referred incorrectly
in some editions to the year Ghana became independent. It was 1957,
not 1960.
