Students listen to first lady Hillary Rodham Clinton during a visit
to their school in Manhattan on Thursday. Mrs. Clinton continued
her visit to the city on Thursday amid increasing speculation about
her possible run for the Senate seat of Sen. Daniel Patrick
Moynihan, a fellow Democrat who is retiring. (James Estrin/New York
Times Photo)
</P>
