Information Technology Laboratories, bounces a ball for a robotic
dog controlled by Aperios, a new operating system that will soon
compete head-on with Microsoft's Windows CE. Such inventions are at
the heart of a battle between Sony and Microsoft, consumer
electronics and PCs, over the future of information technology.
(Stuart Isett/New York Times Photo)
