and brought down Rep. Robert Livingston, who acknowledged having
adulterous affairs, declined to run as speaker of the House, and
has now resigned.
 &HT;    A U.S. News &AMP; World Report cover story reports that in 1996,
''Americans spent more than $8 billion on hardcore videos, peep
shows, live sex acts, adult cable programming, sexual devices,
